---
title: Spiced White Fish & Honey Glaze with Roasted Kohlrabi, Apple Salad & Garlic Hollandaise
description: Golden and glowing, that’s how we like our chicken and the combination of our Aussie spice blend and honey coating
doesn’t disappoint. The roasted parsnip and carrot shine just as bright on the plate, perfect for dipping in a garlic
Hollandaise. Dig in and enjoy, we know you will love it!

